{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Here is a **precision AI prompt** engineered to generate a block that matches your screenshot almost exactly — structure, spacing, proportions, and luxury feel — so you won’t need to manually adjust anything.
    
    Paste this into Shopify **Generate block**.
    
    ---
    
    ## ✅ PERFECT COPY GENERATE PROMPT
    
    Create a luxury editorial section that is visually identical to a high-end jewelry brand “Our Commitments” page.
    
    The layout must follow this exact structure and spacing:
    
    ---
    
    SECTION 1 – INTRO (CENTERED)
    
    • Add a narrow centered text block at the top
    • Maximum width: 720–760px
    • Text aligned center
    • Small refined body font
    • Line height slightly generous (around 1.7–1.8)
    • Large spacing below intro (80–100px)
    
    No heading above it.
    
    ---
    
    SECTION 2 – TWO COLUMN GRID (FIRST ROW)
    
    Create a two-column layout:
    
    Left Column:
    • Landscape image
    • Image fills column width
    • No border
    • No shadow
    
    Right Column:
    • Heading: “The Kimberley Process”
    • Serif-style elegant heading
    • Medium weight (not bold-heavy)
    • Size larger than body but not oversized
    • Paragraph text below heading
    • Clean spacing between heading and paragraph
    
    Columns:
    • Equal width (50% / 50%)
    • Large horizontal gap (70–90px)
    • Vertically centered alignment
    • Generous bottom spacing (100px)
    
    ---
    
    SECTION 3 – TWO COLUMN GRID (SECOND ROW)
    
    Create another two-column layout directly underneath:
    
    Left Column:
    • Heading: “Responsible Jewellery Council”
    • Paragraph text underneath
    • Same typography and spacing as previous section
    
    Right Column:
    • Landscape image
    • Same proportions as first image
    • Same height style as previous image
    
    Columns:
    • Equal width
    • Same horizontal spacing as above
    • Vertically centered
    • Large spacing below section (100px)
    
    ---
    
    SECTION 4 – GREY BACKGROUND SECTION
    
    Add a full-width section with a very light grey background.
    
    Inside it create a two-column layout:
    
    Left Column:
    • Large horizontal image
    • Image occupies majority width
    • No overlay
    • No border
    
    Right Column:
    • Heading: “Associations & Organizations”
    • Smaller than main headings above
    • Under heading add short paragraph description
    • Below paragraph add vertical list of association names
    • No bullet icons
    • Small refined uppercase text
    • Slight letter spacing
    • Generous spacing between list items
    
    Columns:
    • Left column slightly wider (about 60% image / 40% text)
    • Large horizontal spacing
    • Vertically aligned center
    
    ---
    
    BUTTON
    
    At bottom of grey section:
    • Centered outline button
    • Text: “View More Ethical Initiatives”
    • Thin black border
    • Transparent background
    • Uppercase letters
    • Letter spacing increased
    • Medium padding
    • On hover: black background with white text
    
    ---
    
    STYLING REQUIREMENTS
    
    • Editorial luxury aesthetic
    • Minimalist
    • No shadows
    • No animations
    • No decorative lines
    • Clean spacing hierarchy
    • White background for first sections
    • Very light grey background for association section
    • Fully responsive
    • On mobile: stack columns vertically
    • Maintain correct order:
    
    * First section image above text
    * Second section text above image
    
    The design must look balanced, symmetrical, refined, and high-end — like a luxury jewelry maison website.
    
    Do not add extra elements.
    Do not add icons.
    Do not change typography hierarchy.
    Keep proportions visually elegant and consistent.
    
    ---
    
    If you want, I can also give you an even more technical prompt with pixel-level spacing values to make it even closer to the screenshot.
    
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-commitments-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-commitments-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 40px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-commitments-intro-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto {{ block.settings.intro_spacing }}px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-commitments-intro-{{ ai_gen_id }} p {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.intro_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.intro_line_height }};
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-commitments-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: {{ block.settings.column_gap }}px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.row_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commitments-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-commitments-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: {{ block.settings.image_aspect_ratio }};
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-commitments-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-commitments-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-commitments-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.heading_spacing }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-commitments-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.body_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.body_line_height }};
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-commitments-grey-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.grey_bg_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.grey_section_padding }}px 0;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.grey_section_margin_top }}px;
  }

  .ai-commitments-grey-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }

  .ai-commitments-grey-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: {{ block.settings.grey_column_gap }}px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.grey_content_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commitments-associations-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-commitments-associations-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.associations_heading_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.associations_heading_spacing }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-commitments-associations-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.body_font_size }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.body_line_height }};
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.list_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commitments-list-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-commitments-list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.list_font_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.list_letter_spacing }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.list_item_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commitments-button-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-commitments-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal }}px;
    background-color: transparent;
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    border: {{ block.settings.button_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.button_border_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.button_letter_spacing }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_font_size }}px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-commitments-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .ai-commitments-container-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-commitments-grey-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.6 }}px 20px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .ai-commitments-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .ai-commitments-grey-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .ai-commitments-text-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-commitments-associations-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .ai-commitments-intro-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .ai-commitments-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-commitments-associations-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.associations_heading_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<commitments-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-commitments-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-commitments-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.intro_text != blank %}
      <div class="ai-commitments-intro-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.intro_text }}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-commitments-row-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-commitments-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.image_1 %}
          <img
            src="{{ block.settings.image_1 | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
            alt="{{ block.settings.image_1.alt | escape }}"
            loading="lazy"
            width="{{ block.settings.image_1.width }}"
            height="{{ block.settings.image_1.height }}"
            class="ai-commitments-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-commitments-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="ai-commitments-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.heading_1 != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-commitments-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading_1 }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.paragraph_1 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-commitments-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph_1 }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-commitments-row-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-commitments-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.heading_2 != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-commitments-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading_2 }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.paragraph_2 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-commitments-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph_2 }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="ai-commitments-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.image_2 %}
          <img
            src="{{ block.settings.image_2 | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
            alt="{{ block.settings.image_2.alt | escape }}"
            loading="lazy"
            width="{{ block.settings.image_2.width }}"
            height="{{ block.settings.image_2.height }}"
            class="ai-commitments-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-commitments-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ai-commitments-grey-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-commitments-grey-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-commitments-grey-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <div class="ai-commitments-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.associations_image %}
            <img
              src="{{ block.settings.associations_image | image_url: width: 1400 }}"
              alt="{{ block.settings.associations_image.alt | escape }}"
              loading="lazy"
              width="{{ block.settings.associations_image.width }}"
              height="{{ block.settings.associations_image.height }}"
              class="ai-commitments-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
          {% else %}
            <div class="ai-commitments-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="ai-commitments-associations-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.associations_heading != blank %}
            <h3 class="ai-commitments-associations-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.associations_heading }}</h3>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.associations_description != blank %}
            <div class="ai-commitments-associations-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.associations_description }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if block.settings.association_1 != blank or block.settings.association_2 != blank or block.settings.association_3 != blank or block.settings.association_4 != blank or block.settings.association_5 != blank %}
            <ul class="ai-commitments-list-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if block.settings.association_1 != blank %}
                <li class="ai-commitments-list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.association_1 }}</li>
              {% endif %}
              {% if block.settings.association_2 != blank %}
                <li class="ai-commitments-list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.association_2 }}</li>
              {% endif %}
              {% if block.settings.association_3 != blank %}
                <li class="ai-commitments-list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.association_3 }}</li>
              {% endif %}
              {% if block.settings.association_4 != blank %}
                <li class="ai-commitments-list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.association_4 }}</li>
              {% endif %}
              {% if block.settings.association_5 != blank %}
                <li class="ai-commitments-list-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.association_5 }}</li>
              {% endif %}
            </ul>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
      {% if block.settings.button_text != blank %}
        <div class="ai-commitments-button-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <a href="{{ block.settings.button_link }}" class="ai-commitments-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.button_text }}
          </a>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</commitments-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class CommitmentsSection{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }
    }
    customElements.define('commitments-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}', CommitmentsSection{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
